{"tid":1592032,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於101大戰。。","createTime":"2019-09-24T12:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T16:02:30.000Z","uid":153250,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a23c1b0cffc555d4881f7dc5949bcf6ec0cb963d","tid":1592032,"uid":153250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<br />\n101百萬大遊行，唔係話唔得，而係點解明明一早講好偏地開花而家轉?<br />\n9月頭個時大家話101係大決戰<br />\n到而家未又係得個遊行?<br />\n好啦遊行，最後一定會演變成煲底＞退銅記＞天后被人包<br />\n我就想問有咩意思呢?<br />\n<br />\n8月5個日係閒日，都召集到咁多人搞5區<br />\n你唸唸101係紅日，呢日一定仲多人過8月5<br />\n同埋8月5政府係驚到賴屎，警力分散<br />\n個日算係成功，有咩理由唔搞5區?<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話101百萬遊行可以製造國際討論，落阿爺面<br />\n我想講中共不嬲係國際笑柄，佢都被人笑慣，到而家3個月，你覺得佢仲care呢啲野?<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，吹雞101遊行既人係想製造一個門面效果，睇落去好盛大，其實實則效果係咩大家心知吐明，華而不實"},{"pid":"4a8def0719d531ed7b27c069522aabb1a942cb8e","tid":1592032,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"8d8fc49d447b896f46e783047c8e30561d7bbadc","tid":1592032,"uid":153250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"842fcffc923a226a40eca5552890858a8f2b0f85","tid":1592032,"uid":153250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e96ec205e8a0842019be1d14bf1e281c31899677","tid":1592032,"uid":308406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9aa4daf7bf5ef2cbe644e9e2e6c68065ab80f41b","tid":1592032,"uid":289185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"929 / 101 民主護旗手<br />\n<br />\n旗已經買晒兼到齊，依家要人！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thr